edu.umn.nlpengine

Interface ArtifactTask


  • public ArtifactTask

    An operation to be run once on every artifact run through the processing pipeline. One instance is created per interface Artifact and ArtifactTask.run is called once per instance.

    See Also:
    interface Artifact, ArtifactTask.run

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Default Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void run(Artifact artifact)
      Performs the processing on the artifact this operation is responsible for processing.
